main event: Multiple witnesses observed bright green UFOs during the Gemini 5 launch near Cape Kennedy, Florida, on August 21, 1965.
interesting points: James R. Peak photographed three unidentified flying objects shortly after the Gemini 5 launch., The UFOs appeared as brilliant green phosphorescent lights., Witnesses reported that the UFOs were seen moving at high speeds near the rocket launch area., The photographs were initially believed to show film defects but were later confirmed to depict actual UFOs., These sightings triggered interest and inquiry into the nature of the objects.
witness description: James R. Peak and his three sons observed the UFOs during the launch.
